        Co-Owned Property and One Owner Won't Sell: Your Options in Queensland
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        You cannot sell co-owned property without the other owner's consent, but you are not without options. Here is what the law allows and what works in practice.
      </p>
